  <main class="container" role="main" aria-label="Home improvement services">
    <h1>Home Improvement Services</h1>
    <p>Enhance your home with our expert improvement services. Whether you're looking to renovate, remodel, or simply refresh your space, we have the solutions for you.</p>

    <div class="tips">
      <h2>Home Improvement Tips</h2>
      <p>1. Start with a plan: Define your goals and budget before beginning any project.</p>
      <p>2. Choose quality materials: Invest in durable materials that will stand the test of time.</p>
      <p>3. Hire professionals: For major renovations, consider hiring licensed contractors to ensure quality work.</p>
      <p>4. Focus on energy efficiency: Look for ways to improve your home's energy efficiency, such as insulation and energy-efficient appliances.</p>
      <p>5. Don't forget curb appeal: Simple landscaping and exterior updates can significantly enhance your home's value.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="request-form">
      <h2>Request a Consultation</h2>
      <form id="improvement-request-form" aria-label="Request home improvement consultation" action="improvement-request-form" method="post">
        <div>
          <label for="name">Your Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="email">Email Address</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
          <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required placeholder="Tell us about your project..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" aria-label="Submit request for consultation">
          <span class="material-icons" aria-hidden="true">send</span> Submit Request
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
